trans-unit.source: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Biedt een listener die routeert alle tracering en foutopsporing van uitvoer naar de [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructuur.

trans-unit.source: The IisTraceListener class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: De klasse IisTraceListener verbindt het mechanisme voor tracering van [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] naar [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> and <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Deze klasse listener kan ontwikkelaars die maken [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] toepassingen en die implementeren de <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>en <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>interfaces voor paginaniveau, niveau van de module of handler niveau terugpostgebeurtenissen naar de [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] -infrastructuur bij tracering is ingeschakeld.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> </xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Deze klasse listener geen routering [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] gebeurtenissen in ASP.NET-klassen.

trans-unit.source: This includes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class and classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> or <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
trans-unit.target: Dit omvat de <xref:System.Web.UI.Page>klasse en klassen die implementeren de <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule>of <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>interface.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> </xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> </xref:System.Web.UI.Page>
